name: current-time
description:
Returns a list of the current time components:
  (<hour> <minute> <second> <millisecond>)

name: current-date
description:
Returns a list of the current date components:
  (<year> <month> <day>)

name: epoch-time
description: Returns the number of milliseconds since the epoch (1 January 1970).

name: time-zone
description: Returns the name of the current time-zone as a string (#f if unknown).

name: day
description: Returns the name of the current week-day as a string (#f if unknown).

name: month
description: Returns the name of the current month as a string (#f if unknown).

name: year
description: Returns the name of the current year as a string (#f if unknown).
